data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bed, 2 bath ranch in Gretna. Better than new and super clean. Open foyer with engineered wood fls, living room with vault ceiling and fireplace. Opens to kitchen with loads of cabinets, super-sized islands, and SS appl, pantry. Engineered wood fls and an informal dining room that walks out to a deck. Main flr laundry with addl cabinets. Great sized primary bedroom. Primary bath with jet tub and separate shower, generous walk-in closet. Addl bedrooms are great sized for a ranch home. The lower level is awaiting all your finishes. Garage has great shelving built in that will stay. Sprinkler system and water softener. Fresh paint throughout. Home backs to the brand-new YMCA. AMA
